sql:
SELECT
    test_area,
    sms_device,
    srcfab,
    w.test_program,
    v.program,
    v.lot,
    v.fablot,
    w.tester,
    w.prober,
    w.probe_card,
    w.loadbd AS PIB,
    v.wafer_id,
    to_char(w.end_time,'MON/DD/YYYY') AS date_1,
    w.end_time,
    ROUND(SUM(CASE WHEN v.bin IN (1,2,3,4,5) THEN v.total ELSE 0 END) / NULLIF(SUM(v.total), 0) * 100, 2) AS YIELD,
    SUM(CASE WHEN v.bin IN (1,2,3,4,5) THEN v.total ELSE 0 END) AS GOOD_BIN_COUNT,
    COUNT(*) AS Bin_Record_Count
FROM
    vmerge_Bin_zone v
INNER JOIN
    wafer w ON v.lot_seq = w.lot_seq AND v.wafer_id = w.wafer_id
WHERE
    w.tester LIKE 'TT5003%'
    AND w.end_time >= TO_DATE('31-AUG-2025 00:00:00','DD-MON-YYYY HH24:MI:SS')
    AND w.end_time <= TO_DATE('31-AUG-2025 23:59:59','DD-MON-YYYY HH24:MI:SS')
GROUP BY
    sms_device, srcfab, test_area, to_char(w.end_time,'MON/DD/YYYY'),
    v.fablot, v.lot, v.program, v.wafer_id,
    w.end_time, w.loadbd, w.probe_card, w.prober,
    w.test_program, w.tester;
